  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641530/extras/421d9bd2d9d20ca989561bb7ec2c60df.poster.avif?t=1747633261\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641530/extras/421d9bd2d9d20ca989561bb7ec2c60df.webm?t=1747633261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641530/extras/421d9bd2d9d20ca989561bb7ec2c60df.mp4?t=1747633261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>AUTOMATED MESSAGE /// On the Acid Planet, human beings have been all but wiped out. Hordes of bio-monsters run wild and have grown to colossal size. The largest of these beasts are known as Kaiju. <br><br>You are a clone in the service of SCAV Corporation, welcome! You will conduct Kaiju salvage operations from our orbital station. <br><br>Use your automatic defense systems, personal weaponry and drones to repel the swarm until the Kaiju arrives. Your only priority is the capture of the Kaiju cores. You will be re-cloned as required. Good luck! /// END MESSAGE</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641530/extras/dab3493f08c8e72e862580fa5245922e.poster.avif?t=1747633261\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641530/extras/dab3493f08c8e72e862580fa5245922e.webm?t=1747633261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD THE ULTIMATE DEFENSE</h2>Construct towers and drone factories to defend your ship from the horde. Make use of the environment - strategic placement matters. Balance weaponry and defensive structures against developing your upgrades and economy. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641530/extras/9109e8c75c77118240eddccb290f50ae.poster.avif?t=1747633261\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641530/extras/9109e8c75c77118240eddccb290f50ae.webm?t=1747633261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641530/extras/9109e8c75c77118240eddccb290f50ae.mp4?t=1747633261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVE THE DESERT</h2>Move your crew member to help your auto-shooting defenses fight back swarms of enemies. Between waves, meet the denizens of the desert in risk/reward encounters. Survive long enough and you'll face the massive boss Kaiju, each one with unique and devastating abilities. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641530/extras/e8f3a15be11157b23f0bbfe098c62de0.poster.avif?t=1747633261\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641530/extras/e8f3a15be11157b23f0bbfe098c62de0.webm?t=1747633261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641530/extras/e8f3a15be11157b23f0bbfe098c62de0.mp4?t=1747633261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EVOLVE TO PERFECTION</h2>Choose a powerful new ability or upgrade after every wave. Evolve your weapons and towers into strange new forms. Use recovered Kaiju cores to boost your abilities between runs. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641530/extras/b5ad18d3efa11b9ea7497abbc2811c51.poster.avif?t=1747633261\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641530/extras/b5ad18d3efa11b9ea7497abbc2811c51.webm?t=1747633261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641530/extras/b5ad18d3efa11b9ea7497abbc2811c51.mp4?t=1747633261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Action Tower-Defense gameplay with RTS and roguelite elements<br></li><li> Over 50 unique perks, buildings and weapons<br></li><li> Build structures, control your hero and command armies of drones<br></li><li>Fight through 7 missions of controlled chaos, each with unique Kaiju bosses<br></li><li>Post-run meta-progression with 25+ unlockable items<br></li><li>Lovingly hand-drawn pixel art graphics<br></li><li>Original soundtrack by Cletus Lupus</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NEW IN 0.80!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Added Hotshot and Freak difficulties! Use the freak stars to dial it all the way up. <br></li><li>New Encounters mechanic! Meet some of the strange denizens of the desert, with their own risks and rewards. <br></li><li>New perks and stats! Master weapon sub-types, hoard ship back-ups and turtle in with the new Shield Charger support tower. <br><br><br>Acid Planet is best enjoyed with keyboard + mouse, and gamepads are also supported.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641530/extras/bef9be6f8f882bd516d9e2e5b08e7bdb.apng?t=1747633261\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641530/extras/bef9be6f8f882bd516d9e2e5b08e7bdb.poster.avif?t=1747633261\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=135 /></picture></span></li></ul>",
